description.text: Social Media Director at Mount Sinai Health System

commentaryText.text:
I am incredibly proud of my team that continues to strive for social media excellence (Andria Garcia & Suzy Qiu not pictured here). 

Our Social Media Ambassador Program received the Silver in Best Digital Physician Engagement and Platinum for Best in Social Media! 

Launched in early 2020, our ambassador program aims to debunk misinformation spread on social media, inspire patients to live healthier lives, build a robust online community, and much more.

We could not have won these awards without the dedication and efforts from our Mount Sinai social media ambassadors!

#SocialMedia #HCIC #HCSM

text.text: I have had the pleasure of working with MLisa for several years. She is collaborative, creative, and an incredibly talented individual. She has played instrumental roles in the implementation of various social media campaigns at the Icahn School of Medicine, including medical student Instagram takeovers and live event coverage. She is passionate about any project that is assigned to her or she has developed on her own. MLisa's work ethic, responsiveness, and innovative ideas make her a unique member of the marketing team. MLisa's ambition will certainly lead to her doing great things in her career!
